@page "/"

<PageTitle>Welcome</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to AeroNexus Forecast Studio</h1>

<p class="lead">
    The first iteration delivers interactive experiences for group management and the
    statistical and flight schedule import wizards. Use the navigation bar to explore
    these capabilities as we continue modernising the BTactical workflows.
</p>

<div class="row g-3">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5">Group Editor</h2>
                <p>Create reusable filter groups per scenario with ordered condition lists.</p>
                <NavLink class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/groups">Open group editor</NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5">Statistical imports</h2>
                <p>Validate, map, and persist airport statistics for comparison baselines.</p>
                <NavLink class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/imports/statistics">Launch wizard</NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5">Schedule imports</h2>
                <p>Walk through multi-step schedule ingestion with preview and auto-referencing.</p>
                <NavLink class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/imports/schedule">Launch wizard</NavLink>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
